{"tid":1721114,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"旭日行動 方向大整合！","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T19:30:30.000Z","uid":199716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"268518430254b43e0e695f1b278ed9ca45744983","tid":1721114,"uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"各位，今日可以見到政府開始冷處理，我地必須採取行動攻佢要害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解政府可以冷處理？因為我地發動唔到<span style=\"color: red;\">大罷工、大癱瘓</span> 我地有時真係太過戀戰 防暴黎又唔肯走 硬碰硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣可以達到社會停擺效果 強逼政府回應呢？其實最應該就係：<span style=\"color: gold;\">每日朝早 每隔3個站 派20-30人塞鐵 唔洗每個站都派人 節省人手 塞撚爆佢 唔好比佢開</span>車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住其餘人上路面擺roadblock 主要大路、十字路口、巴士電車小巴必經之路 都擺roadblock 唔好比人移開（or 留返一條行車線）<span style=\"color: gold;\">早上7點-11點 塞爆全城 下午放工時間5-8點再次塞爆地面同埋地鐵</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好戀戰 防暴到就走人 去隔黎地區幫手  <span style=\"color: red;\">夜晚8點後全部人返屋企訓覺 食個飽飽飯</span> 夜晚一來少人左 啲狗又更進取 同埋其實再塞效果大大減少 因為好多人已經放工or backed home. <br />\n<br />\n第二朝再次出動塞鐵 塞路面 唔好比佢正常返工 港共必須回應 我肯定！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家我地真係唔可以再拖 否則失民意 甚至自己人都開始迷失 失去方向 加油 光復香港 時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"fcbd35b95e7085bf62ff6ef46c2bcd4a8c384726","tid":1721114,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4793e322a3f895ddc52f66198433d64a378a2231","tid":1721114,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"［旭日行動］唔好太依賴塞鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d321aad41006c55bd31c563082a4e64a2744c57","tid":1721114,"uid":199716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"補充一句 我做銀行分行 哩個禮拜星期一、二 完全做唔到生意 同事好多要遲到 分行又關4點（正常5點）又好少客過黎 數都跑唔到條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係今日條路順翻好多 客都多翻曬 正常時間關門 多翻好多數，所以大癱瘓一定要搞到！否則好多野都白費<br />\n<br />\n我返大公司可能冇咁快唔掂 但係中小企業 一定頂唔順 根本做唔到生意 如果持續2星期政府必要回應 <br />\n<br />\n大家有咩意見 請提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270620f66df6deebf6b6b472ed32e333d3f9ab17","tid":1721114,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cfc65c58e1e0613c4a7aa61ed5d50cd184b095","tid":1721114,"uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"推爆！！！！！"},{"pid":"9f7b6b4583a13cce62da870552de49392a4a75ec","tid":1721114,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c00c240821924b253abeef8df73bcda0f9fb5e","tid":1721114,"uid":109712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"必須有一批人塞大欖出或入口，哩度有元天同新界東北仲想返工的人，幾區總人口加埋接近100萬人！"},{"pid":"478c9b2ed0d40580a5403e89e0f8be032e84860c","tid":1721114,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70e4cdebd7ea8c1dcc22ba839eed706c1080082","tid":1721114,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2007320dfe99abd10c1429b6e36ac147ef72cce2","tid":1721114,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}